            "name": "description",
            "type": "java.lang.String",
            "value": "Zend\\Mvc\\Router\\Http\\Part::assemble (184) line sets option has_child based on if the route has a name or not, instead of whether the route has children.  The has_child option set to true precludes the ability for optional route parameters to be NULL and thus excluded from the assembled route."
